b_buffer_pool\r\nJun 07 17:12:19 keju mariadbd[1959]: 2026-06-07 17:12:19 0 [Note] InnoDB: Buffer pool(s) load completed at 260607 17:12:19\r\nJun 07 17:12:19 keju mariadbd[1959]: 2026-06-07 17:12:19 0 [Note] Server socket created on IP: '0.0.0.0', port: '3306'.\r\nJun 07 17:12:19 keju mariadbd[1959]: 2026-06-07 17:12:19 0 [Note] Server socket created on IP: '::', port: '3306'.\r\nJun 07 17:12:19 keju mariadbd[1959]: 2026-06-07 17:12:19 0 [Note] mariadbd: Event Scheduler: Loaded 0 events\r\nJun 07 17:12:19 keju mariadbd[1959]: 2026-06-07 17:12:19 0 [Note] /usr/bin/mariadbd: ready for connections.\r\nJun 07 17:12:19 keju mariadbd[1959]: Version: '12.3.2-MariaDB'  socket: '/run/mysqld/mysqld.sock'  port: 3306  Arch Linux\r\nJun 07 17:12:19 keju systemd[1]: Started MariaDB 12.3.2 database server.\r\n"]
