[0.000, "o", "\u001b7\u001b[2;65r\u001b8\u001b[65d"]
[0.000, "o", "\n\u001b[1;67r\u001b[64;1H| The $active_group variable lets you choose which connection group to\r"]
[0.034, "o", "\u001b[?25l\u001b[?1c\u001b[?25h\u001b[?0c"]
[0.001, "o", "\u001b7\u001b[2;65r\u001b8\u001b[65d\n\u001b[1;67r\u001b[64;1H| make active.  By default there is only one group (the 'default' group).\r"]
